<h4 id="ç®—æœ¯è¿ç®—arithmetic-operations">ç®—æœ¯è¿ç®—ï¼ˆArithmetic operationsï¼‰</h4>

<ul>
  <li>äºŒå…ƒè¿ç®—ç¬¦ï¼ˆBinary operatorsï¼‰:<code class="highlighter-rouge">+, -, *, /, %</code></li>
  <li>å‡å·ï¼ˆå•ç›®è¿ç®—ç¬¦ï¼‰Minus sign (unary operator):<code class="highlighter-rouge">-</code></li>
