  <li>äºŒå…ƒè¿ç®—ç¬¦ï¼ˆBinary operatorsï¼‰:<code class="highlighter-rouge">and, or</code></li>
  <li>å¸ƒå°”å¦å®šï¼ˆä¸€å…ƒè¿ç®—ç¬¦ï¼‰Boolean negation (unary operator):<code class="highlighter-rouge">!, not</code></li>
